'''可爱多'''（{{lang-it|'''Cornetto'''}}，{{IPA-it|korˈnetto}}）是意式冷冻甜筒品牌，由英国荷兰公司[[联合利华|联合利华]]拥有，屬於[[和路雪|和路雪]]产品系列。

== 名稱 ==
意大利语中的意思是“小喇叭”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.sfgate.com/travel/article/One-Day-One-Place-Eat-up-Rome-during-tourist-8319277.php|title=One Day, One Place: Eat up Rome during tourist season|last=Wach|first=Bonnie|date=2016-06-22|newspaper=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]|access-date=2019-06-05|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220173621/https://www.sfgate.com/travel/article/One-Day-One-Place-Eat-up-Rome-during-tourist-8319277.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，還以不同的名称而享誉国际，包括意大利的Algida，英国的和路雪，爱尔兰共和国的HB<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hbicecream.ie/Brand/Cornetto.aspx|title=Share Happy|publisher=HB Ice Cream|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928205214/http://www.hbicecream.ie/Brand/Cornetto.aspx|archive-date=2015-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，西班牙的Frigo<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.frigo.es/Brand/Brandslist.aspx|title=Comparte Felicidad|publisher=Frigo|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928235738/http://www.frigo.es/Brand/Brandslist.aspx|archive-date=2015-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和印度的Kwality Wall's。

